title: Beyond the Horror: Cult Episode 5
author: MaryGirl Moody
comment: I feel like Meadow, wouldn't have told Ally that Ivy was against her too, if she was faking! I also think Ally believes Meadow.
Episode 3, 4 & 5 were just amazing MaryGirl. This season has really gotten on a roll !.
It's getting so interesting! I agree with Casey that each one gets better! Surprises everywhere!!! Love that Jonas was back again!
We never saw Meadow die so I assume she's alive
I have so many questions after this episode. The biggest being why would Ivy be okay with the cult killing 2 of her employees?
description:
VIDEO CONTAINS SPOILERS FOR American Horror Story, Season 7, Episode 5!!!

Beyond the Horror: Cult, is an unofficial American Horror Story Live After Show. Hosted by MaryGirl Moody. Guests include: Maisie Andrews, Casey Soper, and Jonas Bendor. We discuss and review each episode of American Horror Story Cult.
